="https://www.nme.com/news/music/smashing-pumpkins-announce-13th-album-aghori-mhori-mei-out-next-month-3776469">于八月发行了一张令人惊喜的专辑“Aghori Mhori Mei”</a> ，这是他们总共发行的第 13 张录音室唱片。它仅以数字版本发布，实体版本将于 11 月 22 日发布。</p><p>其他消息中，Corgan 最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billy-corgan-enlists-ai-to-share-videos-with-fans-in-eight-languages-3783732">使用人工智能 (AI) 制作了一个新视频，以八种语言宣传 Smashing Pumpkins 的新专辑</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3612038" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3612038" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3612038" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/smashing-pumpkins@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/smashing-pumpkins@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/smashing-pumpkins@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/smashing-pumpkins@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/smashing-pumpkins@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/smashing-pumpkins@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/smashing-pumpkins@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3612038" class="wp-caption-text">粉碎南瓜乐队的比利·科根。图片来源：杰夫·哈恩/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>上个月，科根在社交媒体上发表了一份对身体积极的声明， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/smashing-pumpkins-billy-corgan-on-his-port-wine-birthmarks-for-body-positivity-and-celebrating-what-makes-us-us-3790205">公开了他的波特酒胎记</a>。他分享说，在他一生的大部分时间里，他都隐藏了自己的胎记，因为小时候他被“无情地”嘲笑。</p><p>他继续说道：“即使是现在，陌生人也会在街上拦住我，不是因为他们认识我，而是因为他们认为我出了什么问题，需要医疗护理。再加上随机的问题：是烧伤吗？你生病了吗？会传染吗？疼吗？</p><p> “今天传达的积极信息是：无论你是谁，我希望你能找到自己的平静，因为：我想认识那个人，而不是其他人。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billy-corgan-announces-solo-australian-tour-for-winter-2024-3807310">Billy Corgan 宣布 2024 年冬季单独澳大利亚巡演的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀谈杰里米·艾伦·怀特传记片的选角：“我知道他是合适的人选” https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-on-jeremy-allen-whites-casting-in-biopic-i-knew-he-was-the-right-guy-3807303?utm_source= rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=bruce-springsteen-on-jeremy-allen-whites-cast-in-传记片-我知道他是对的人Surej SinghTue, 29 Oct 2024 04:00:35 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3807303 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jeremy-allen-white@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jeremy-allen-white@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jeremy-allen-white@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jeremy-allen-white@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jeremy-allen-white@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jeremy-allen-white@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jeremy-allen-white@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>昨天分享了怀特扮演老板的第一眼</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-on-jeremy-allen-whites-casting-in-biopic-i-knew-he-was-the-right-guy-3807303">布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀 (Bruce Springsteen) 关于杰里米·艾伦·怀特 (Jeremy Allen White) 传记片选角的帖子：“我知道他是合适的人选”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jeremy-allen-white@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jeremy-allen-white@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jeremy-allen-white@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jeremy-allen-white@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jeremy-allen-white@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jeremy-allen-white@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jeremy-allen-white@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruce-springsteen">布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀</a>分享了他对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jeremy-allen-white">杰里米·艾伦·怀特</a>在即将上映的传记片<em>《从无处拯救我》</em>中扮演“老板”的想法。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-features/music-biopics-best-to-see-before-you-die-3401944"><b>生前值得一看的 50 部音乐传记片</b></a></li></ul><p>昨天（10 月 28 日）， <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/the-bear"><em>《熊》</em></a>主演杰里米·艾伦·怀特饰演年轻的布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/jeremy-allen-white-transforms-into-bruce-springsteen-in-first-look-at-new-biopic-3806993">首次正式</a>亮相。在下面的图片中，怀特穿着 The Boss 标志性的法兰绒和牛仔夹克造型，双手插在口袋里。</p><p>在最近接受<a href="https://www.telegraph.co.uk/music/interviews/bruce-springsteen-interview-trump-is-mentally-unstable/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《每日电讯报》</em></a>采访时，斯普林斯汀被问及怀特的选角问题。老板回复道，解释怀特是这个角色的“合适人选”：“我只在<em>《熊》</em>中看到了他，我就知道他是合适的人选，因为他有那种内心生活，但他也有一点狂妄。 ”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3807026" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3807026" style="width: 1999px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3807026" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jeremy-Allen-White-as-Bruce-Springsteen-in-Deliver-Me-From-Nowhere.jpg" alt="杰里米·艾伦·怀特在《从无处拯救我》中饰演布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀" width="1999" height="3000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jeremy-Allen-White-as-Bruce-Springsteen-in-Deliver-Me-From-Nowhere.jpg 1999w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jeremy-Allen-White-as-Bruce-Springsteen-in-Deliver-Me-From-Nowhere-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jeremy-Allen-White-as-Bruce-Springsteen-in-Deliver-Me-From-Nowhere-800x1201.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jeremy-Allen-White-as-Bruce-Springsteen-in-Deliver-Me-From-Nowhere-696x1045.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jeremy-Allen-White-as-Bruce-Springsteen-in-Deliver-Me-From-Nowhere-1392x2089.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jeremy-Allen-White-as-Bruce-Springsteen-in-Deliver-Me-From-Nowhere-1068x1603.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1999px) 100vw, 1999px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3807026" class="wp-caption-text">杰里米·艾伦·怀特 (Jeremy Allen White) 在《从无处拯救我》中饰演布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀 (Bruce Springsteen)。图片来源：华特迪士尼工作室</figcaption></figure><p>斯普林斯汀的长期导师兼经理乔恩·兰道补充说，扮演“老板”会看到怀特“描绘出一个非常内向的人。总是有大量的事情在发生，其中一些被阐明，而另一些则被抑制。”</p><p>在影片中，兰道将由<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/succession"><em>《继承之战</em></a>》的杰里米·斯特朗饰演。此后，兰多与斯特朗交谈，并向他提供了以下建议：“我确实告诉他，就他的体重而言，他不需要在角色发展上完全融入《愤怒的公牛》。”斯普林斯汀插话，开玩笑说电影制片人“试图让[斯特朗]穿上肥大的衣服”。</p><p>怀特在<em>《无处可逃》</em>中饰演斯普林斯汀的消息<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jeremy-allen-white-to-reportedly-play-bruce-springsteen-in-nebraska-film-3615030">最早是在四月份报道的</a>。这部电影定于明年上映，将探讨斯普林斯汀 1982 年标志性专辑《内布拉斯加》的制作过程。 </p><figure id="attachment_3805279" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3805279" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3805279" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jon-landau-jim-spellman-1-1.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jon-landau-jim-spellman-1-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jon-landau-jim-spellman-1-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jon-landau-jim-spellman-1-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jon-landau-jim-spellman-1-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jon-landau-jim-spellman-1-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jon-landau-jim-spellman-1-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3805279" class="wp-caption-text">纽约，纽约 – 5 月 6 日：歌手/词曲作者 Bruce Springsteen 和音乐制作人 Jon Landau 出席 2017 年 5 月 6 日在纽约市 Tribeca Grill 举行的 2017 年 Kristen Ann Carr 基金“难忘之夜”晚会。 （吉姆·斯佩尔曼/盖蒂图片社拍摄）</figcaption></figure><p>除了《White and Strong》之外， <em>《Deliver Me From Nowhere》</em>还将由<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/stephen-graham-cast-as-bruce-springsteens-dad-in-new-biopic-deliver-me-from-nowhere-3797885"><em>《浴血黑帮》的</em>史蒂文·格雷厄姆</a>饰演斯普林斯汀的父亲， <em>《黑鸟》的</em>保罗·沃尔特·豪瑟将饰演吉他技术人员迈克·巴特兰。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/bruce-springsteens-manager-says-jeremy-allen-white-is-perfect-choice-to-lead-biopic-3805265">最近，现实生活中的兰道在谈到怀特的表演时</a>告诉<em><a href="https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/bruce-springsteen-manager-jon-landau-jeremy-allen-white-biopic-1236040849/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《好莱坞报道》</a> ：</em> “天哪，他太完美了。选角很棒。 [导演]斯科特[库珀]一开始就对我说，‘我们找到了合适的演员，我们会正确地讲述这个故事’，他找到了合适的演员。”</p><p>八月，怀特<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/jeremy-allen-white-says-bruce-springsteen-biopic-prep-includes-going-down-a-youtube-rabbit-hole-3788125">谈到了为这个角色做的准备</a>，他解释道：“我真的很幸运，现在有一个团队可以帮助年轻演员扮演摇滚明星。我有一群非常有才华的人帮助我训练声音和音乐，为这件事做好准备。” </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/film/jeremy-allen-white-transforms-into-bruce-springsteen-in-first-look-at-new-biopic-3806993"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p>他补充说，斯普林斯汀“非常支持这个项目”，并称这位摇滚偶像“只是最伟大的人”。</p></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-on-jeremy-allen-whites-casting-in-biopic-i-knew-he-was-the-right-guy-3807303">布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀 (Bruce Springsteen) 关于杰里米·艾伦·怀特 (Jeremy Allen White) 传记片选角的帖子：“我知道他是合适的人选”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
