swift@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eminem-kid-rock-taylor-swift@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eminem-kid-rock-taylor-swift@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eminem-kid-rock-taylor-swift@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eminem-kid-rock-taylor-swift@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kid-rock">Kid Rock</a>谈到了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eminem">阿姆</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>支持<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/kamala-harris">卡玛拉·哈里斯</a>竞选美国总统 - 看看这位说唱歌手在下面怎么说。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/eminem-the-death-of-slim-shady-coup-de-grace-album-review-3774875">埃米纳姆 – 《The Death of Slim Shady (Coup De Grâce)》评论：精心制作的歌曲和空洞的挑衅</a></strong></li></ul><p>九月，泰勒·斯威夫特<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-announces-endorsement-of-kamala-harris-for-president-3792514">宣布支持卡玛拉·哈里斯</a>。埃米纳姆上周<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/obama-raps-lose-yourself-verse-at-kamala-harris-rally-after-being-introduced-by-eminem-3805325">出席哈里斯底特律集会并介绍了前总统巴拉克·奥巴马</a>时证实了他的支持。 </p><figure id="attachment_3807298" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3807298" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3807298" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/obama-eminem@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/obama-eminem@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/obama-eminem@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/obama-eminem@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/obama-eminem@2000x1270-6