script async src="//platform.instagram.com/en_US/embeds.js"></script></p><p>上周， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-payne-reportedly-had-pink-cocaine-and-other-substances-in-his-system-at-time-of-death-3804922">据报道，佩恩在阳台坠落身亡时，体内含有粉红色可卡因和其他几种物质</a>。消息人士告诉<a href="https://abcnews.go.com/GMA/Culture/liam-payne-partial-autopsy-report-multiple-substances/story?id=114985701" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>美国广播公司新闻</em></a>，部分尸检结果显示，他体内含有“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/colombias-pink-cocaine-reportedly-spreading-through-europe-3365579">粉红可卡因</a>”——一种通常由甲基苯丙胺、氯胺酮、摇头丸等物质混合而成的药物——以及可卡因、苯二氮卓类药物和快克。另据报道，布宜诺斯艾利斯警察局<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/argentinian-police-raid-hotel-where-liam-payne-died-3806078">突击搜查了卡萨苏尔酒店，以寻找进一步的证据</a>。</p><p>佩恩的去世引发了关于为年轻艺术家提供更多保护的讨论，歌曲作家<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/guy-chambers-calls-on-the-music-industry-to-stop-putting-teenagers-in-pop-groups-following-liam-paynes-death-3804414">盖伊·钱伯斯在他去世后呼吁音乐产业停止让未成年人加入男孩乐队</a>。佩恩第一次参加<em>《X Factor》</em>试镜时年仅 14 岁，在节目第 10 季期间成为 One Direction 成员时年仅 16 岁。 </p><figure id="attachment_3805683" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3805683" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3805683" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-1.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3805683" class="wp-caption-text">利亚姆·佩恩.图片来源：Andrew Chin/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>在其他地方，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Sharon-Osbourne">莎朗·奥斯本</a>也<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sharon-osbourne-accuses-music-industry-of-letting-down-liam-payne-3803983">指责音乐产业“让佩恩失望”</a> ，她在 Instagram 上发帖写道：“利亚姆，我的心很痛。我们都让你失望了。当你需要他们的时候这个行业在哪里？当你进入世界上最艰难的行业之一时，你还只是个孩子。谁在你的角落里？安息吧我的朋友。”</p><p>布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀还表示，佩恩去世后，音乐产业“给年轻人带来了巨大的压力”，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Victoria-Canal">维多利亚·卡纳尔</a>也表示， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/victoria-canal-on-the-lethality-of-the-internet-and-liam-payne-just-days-before-his-death-liam-was-relentlessly-torn-apart-online-for-dancing-at-niall-horans-show-3804204">作为一名“绝望”想要实现佩恩曾经取得的成功的艺术家，感觉被欺骗了“这个行业‘成功’的承诺是什么。”</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-paynes-death-petition-safeguarding-mental-health-artists-3805132">此后发起了一份新的请愿书，呼吁制定新的法律来保障音乐行业艺术家的心理健康</a>。请愿书已获得超过10万签名。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-paynes-first-posthumous-song-to-release-this-week-3807292">利亚姆·佩恩本周发布的第一首遗作歌曲</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
